text: Gammelstaden or Gammelstad (Luleå Old Town) is a locality in Luleå Municipality in Norrbotten County in Sweden. In 2010, 4,960 people lived there. The Gammelstad Church Town became a UNESCO World Heritage Site in 1996. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website of the World Heritage Site Gammelstad Church Town Category:Settlements in Norrbotten County
